  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840780/extras/ce18a978ecb112b01177015cef387263.avif?t=1644768238\" width=600 height=75 /></span><br><br>Dannet wants to become a knight. But it turned out that he ended up in the worst-scoring group.<br><br>A bit different approach to Visual Novel with multiple dating events and endings.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >In this game you can:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Try becoming a knight!<br></li><li>Get into suggestive situations!<br></li><li>Change your mind about becoming a knight!<br></li><li>Spend time with the girls!</li></ul><br>The game has about 2 hours of content (All character routes. Depending on your reading speed).",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1840780/extras/ce18a978ecb112b01177015cef387263.avif?t=1644768238\" width=600 height=75 /></span><br><br>Dannet wants to become a knight. But it turned out that he ended up in the worst-scoring group.<br><br>A bit different approach to Visual Novel with multiple dating events and endings.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >In this game you can:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Try becoming a knight!<br></li><li>Get into suggestive situations!<br></li><li>Change your mind about becoming a knight!<br></li><li>Spend time with the girls!</li></ul><br>The game has about 2 hours of content (All character routes. Depending on your reading speed).",
